@startuml
actor "客户端" as Client
participant "认证中心\n(Authentication Center)" as AuthCenter #LightBlue
participant "网关\n(Gateway)" as Gateway #LavenderBlush2
database "缓存\n(Cache/Redis)" as Cache #PaleGreen1
rectangle "业务服务\n(Business Service)" as BusinessService #Thistle

Client -> AuthCenter : 1. 登录请求(用户名密码)
AuthCenter --> Client : 返回 JWT Token (含签名、有效期等)\nHeader.Payload.Signature

note right of Client: **JWT结构示例**\n{\n    \"alg\": \"HS56\",\n    \"typ\": \"JWT\"\n}\n---\n{\n   \"sub\":\"用户ID\", \n   \"exp\":过期时间戳,\n   ...其他声明...\n}


group Authentication & Authorization Flow over HTTPS/TLS
    
    note left of Gateway:\u8BF7\u6C42\u90FD\u5E26HTTPS/\u30B5\u30FC\u30D0\u30A4\u30BA\uFF0F\u30BB\u30AD\u30E5\u30EA\u30C6\u30A3\u30FB\u30EC\u30A4\u30E4\u30FC(TCP+SSL)/TLSvX.X(X>=Y.YYYZ...etc.) + HTTP(S).header["Authorization"] = Bearer <token> 

    
        activate Client
        
            loop Every Request to Protected Resource via API GW
            
